'''Rogue Squadron Headquarters''' was the headquarters for the New Republic fighter unit [[Rogue Squadron/Legends|Rogue Squadron]]. Located on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]], it contained hangars for the squadron's [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|X-wings]], as well as living quarters and offices.

It represented a major shift from the temporary headquarters, like the [[Blackmoon]] or [[Redemption/Legends|''Redemption'']], used until the retaking of Coruscant.

